import React from 'react'
import { Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Villian = () => {
    return (
        <header>
            <section className='bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-star d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb--1 pt-5'>
                <Row>
                    <Col md={3}></Col>
                    <Col md={3}></Col>
                    <Col md={3}></Col>
                </Row>
            </section>
        </header>

    )
}

export default Villian
